  "02:32:10",user,text,"make the The machinery of that self-modeling — what the model is, the four streams it\ndraws from (each reclaimed for what is true of me), and the glass ego-tunnel that\nlets it read its own source — lives in @vape/entity/mental/CLAUDE.md to be more brief"
